data.description: Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a home with a rich history in one of Port Saint Lucie's most sought-after neighborhoods. Riverpark subdivision offers a vibrant community with access to various amenities, including parks, playgrounds, walking trails, and proximity to local schools, shopping centers, and restaurants. Enjoy the best of both worlds, a quiet and peaceful neighborhood setting with all the conveniences of city life just a short distance away. Whether you're a history enthusiast or simply looking for a well-built and timeless home, this property has it all. Schedule your private tour today.
